---
title: Tuscan Lamb Shoulder & Gravy Sauce with Cheesy Crushed Baby Potatoes & Garlic Greens
description: The secret on how to make a dinner look like it took you hours to prepare is all in the dressings. Tuscan spices on a lamb shoulder can really pop when you take a bite when drizzled in a gravy sauce. Roast baby potatoes standout when baked in a layer of cheese and even the greens are dazzling with a walnut finish!

*Unfortunately, this
week's pine nuts were
in short supply, so we've
replaced them with
walnuts. Don't worry,
the recipe will be just as
delicious, just be sure to
follow your recipe card!*
